{"id": "art-245", "label": "Art. 245", "title": "Art. 245", "slug": "art-245", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 245 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_453344671\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1770\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_453344671\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Administratorii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nabsorbite sau ai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care este\ndivizat&#259; r&#259;spund civil <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> sau <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\nacelei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> pentru <span class=SpellE>neregularit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncomise în preg&#259;tirea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> realizarea fuziunii\nsau diviz&#259;rii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_647188239\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1769\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_647188239\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Exper&#355;ii</span> care întocmesc\nraportul prev&#259;zut la art. 243<sup>3</sup>, pe seama <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nabsorbite sau divizate, r&#259;spund civil <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>/<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\nacestor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>neregularit&#259;&#355;ile</span> comise în îndeplinirea\nîndatoririlor lor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}